###############################
# AI Development Notes        #
###############################

# This .gitignore is optimized for AI development tools like Claude Code by:
#
# 1. EXCLUDING heavy files that don't provide AI value:
#    - Build artifacts (bin/, obj/)
#    - Large test datasets
#    - Generated binaries
#    - IDE-specific cache files
#
# 2. INCLUDING files that provide AI context:
#    - All source code (.cs, .csproj)
#    - Documentation and specifications
#    - Configuration samples
#    - Small test data samples
#    - Performance baseline files
#    - CI/CD configuration
#
# 3. BALANCING repository size vs AI effectiveness:
#    - Keep essential context files under 100KB each
#    - Exclude >1MB files unless critical for AI understanding
#    - Preserve project structure visibility
#    - Maintain build reproducibility
#
# This approach ensures Claude Code and other AI tools have sufficient
# context to understand the project while keeping the repository clean
# and focused on source code rather than generated artifacts.